:- Canonical commands: `/interface:design`, `/interface:foundations`, `/interface:motion`, `/interface:audit`, and `/interface:design-reference`. These are the sole public design command surface; the former `/design:*` alias namespace is retired.\n.opencode/skills/sk-design/README.md:70:The canonical creation surface maps `/interface:{design,foundations,motion,audit,design-reference}` to the stable `interface`, `foundations`, `motion`, `audit`, and `md-generator` modes. All five commands share [`shared/creation-contract.md`](./shared/creation-contract.md). The former `/design:*` alias namespace is retired — `/interface:*` is the sole creation surface.\n","exit":0,"truncated":false},"title":"cd /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0092-deep-review-session-shipped-work && grep -nE \"/design:|:design|design:\" .opencode/skills/sk-design/SKILL.md .opencode/skills/sk-design/README.md 2>&1 | head -40","time":{"start":1784606548452,"end":1784606548454}},"id":"prt_f82d6e1d5001q8rB5q8L1Ushb6","sessionID":"ses_07d2d665dffedyOb0L7GbCTElX","messageID":"msg_f82d6d149001pRX2JbQ0PJGjs0"}}
