{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784606680369,"sessionID":"ses_07d2d665dffedyOb0L7GbCTElX","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"call_019f82d8e4277300b9d0f6cb","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"cd /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0092-deep-review-session-shipped-work && grep -nE \"REQ-005|^## \" .opencode/specs/sk-doc/020-hyphen-naming-convention/003-create-generators-and-templates/001-create-skill-and-packaging/spec.md 2>&1 | head -20"},"output":"35:## 1. METADATA\n49:## 2. PROBLEM & PURPOSE\n57:## 3. SCOPE\n74:## 4. REQUIREMENTS\n82:| REQ-005 | Packaging preserves the canonical generated relative paths | The archive filename and archive root use the hyphenated skill name, and a generated temporary tree contains no non-exempt underscore path segment. |\n87:## 5. SUCCESS CRITERIA\n94:## 6. RISKS & DEPENDENCIES\n100:## 7. OPEN QUESTIONS\n","metadata":{"output":"35:## 1. METADATA\n49:## 2. PROBLEM & PURPOSE\n57:## 3. SCOPE\n74:## 4. REQUIREMENTS\n82:| REQ-005 | Packaging preserves the canonical generated relative paths | The archive filename and archive root use the hyphenated skill name, and a generated temporary tree contains no non-exempt underscore path segment. |\n87:## 5. SUCCESS CRITERIA\n94:## 6. RISKS & DEPENDENCIES\n100:## 7. OPEN QUESTIONS\n","exit":0,"truncated":false},"title":"cd /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0092-deep-review-session-shipped-work && grep -nE \"REQ-005|^## \" .opencode/specs/sk-doc/020-hyphen-naming-convention/003-create-generators-and-templates/001-create-skill-and-packaging/spec.md 2>&1 | head -20","time":{"start":1784606680366,"end":1784606680367}},"id":"prt_f82d8e4a3001UGF2OsH3sppmxq","sessionID":"ses_07d2d665dffedyOb0L7GbCTElX","messageID":"msg_f82d8ca36001JTzZvKGn00IPTI"}}
